Custom Configuration Framework (custom-conf)
============================================
Package: custom-conf-ipv6-static

This package provides standard configuration of the IPv6 stack when used along
static addressing.

In particular, it addresses standard configuration of:
 - disabling StateLess Address AutoConfiguration (SLAAC)
 - disabling Duplicate Address Detection (DAD)
 - disabling Router Advertisements (RA) and Solicitations (RS)
 - disabling temporary addresses

